data.text:
Are you looking for the best private label eyelash extension manufacturer in China? If so, then this blog post is for you. We have compiled the best 10 manufacturers that we think are best in the industry and briefly described what they offer. Take a look below to see if one of these companies is the best fit for your needs!

Focus Lashes

Located in Qingdao, Focus Lashes is a leading private label manufacturer that creates and sells quality lashes for 11 years. They provide a service that is fast, simple to order, and does not cost much.

If you are looking for a supplier with the best customer service, they are the right choice. Focus Lashes prides itself on having top-of-line products, and they are best known for the top private label solutions. They also offer the best wholesale prices with small MOQ that you won’t find anywhere else!

Hollyren Cosmetics

Hollyren Cosmetics Co., Ltd is a professional lash products supplier in China with ISO9001 certification. They specialize in false eyelashes and have more than ten years of OEM and ODM experience.

Because of excellent raw materials, standard production procedure, and outstanding after-sale service, the items have been trendy in the worldwide market, mainly Europe, the United States, the Middle East, and Japan.

Babil Lashes

Babil lashes was a 4 people team in 2017, but now they have over 60 people.

Like Focus Lashes, they focus on manufacturing lash extensions only. Their materials are imported from Korea, and the quality is top-notch.

They can currently sell 60K-80K boxes of eyelash extensions per month and have exclusive agents in the Iran market.

CK Beauty Co.,Ltd

Qingdao CK Beauty Co., Ltd is one of the top eyelash extension manufacturers for private label solutions. Their main clients are chain salons from Europe.

With over 10 years of experience, CK Beauty is committed to creating, manufacturing, and supplying prime quality products in the fields of eyelashes, eyelash glue, eyelash kits, and eyelash supplies.

Shanghai Lichu Bio-tech Co., Ltd

Nagaraku is the brand of Shanghai Lichu Bio-tech Co., Ltd. It is one of the best-selling brands for low price eyelash extensions.

Lichu’s factory covers 20000 square meters and over 100 staff. Their products have passed MSDS and SGS.

JTFIL Eyelashes

JTFIL Eyelashes is a Qingdao-based company founded in 2016 and specializes in the distribution and sale of professional eyelashes. In its first three years, the business has grown from one person to over 20 individuals.

Now the company includes sales organizations, physical factories, and design studios. And the factory has two production centers with over 50 workers.

Gollee Cosmetics

Gollee Cosmetics Limited is another Chinese top private label lash extensions manufacturer. They offer the market eyelash goods in complete ranges, including eyelash extensions, glue eyelash tools, and others.

Their sales team is very good at following up on orders. They also provide customers with the best pre-sale and after-sale service.

Aside from the strong sales team, they do a unique design service for the customers as well. Their design team will give you a full branding service to assist your company to grow.

Emeda Arts & Craft Co., Ltd

Emeda Arts & Craft Co., Ltd started in 2000 and has taken on 230 workers since then. They manufacture both artificial eyelashes and human hair. The factory has 80 workers for eyelashes, including 8 supervisors, 12 technicians, and 60 regular laborers.

This company is very picky about its employees. It wants employees who have 10 years of experience in their field and a deep understanding of it.

Sky Eyelash

Sky eyelash is also located in Qingdao. They specialize in eyelash extensions and 3D strip lashes. In recent years, their factory has introduced much sophisticated equipment.

The company wholesales false eyelashes from 2000. They can support small MOQ and quick lead time like Focus Lashes as well.

Obeya Beauty

Obeya Beauty is best known for its cheap private label lashes solution. They were founded in 2002, and they have worked with good retailers and salons.

From 2020, they are starting to sell the products on the Amazon platform.

Conclusion

There are many private label eyelash extension suppliers in China, but these ten manufacturers stand out from the rest. They have years of experience in the industry and can provide you with high-quality products.
